abstract: Neil Genzlinger reviews BBC America crime series Whitechapel, starring Rupert Perry-Jones.
snippet: In “Whitechapel,” a new crime series on BBC America, gruesome murders mimic the Jack the Ripper killings of the 1880s.
lead_paragraph: In “Whitechapel,” a new crime series on BBC America, gruesome murders mimic the Jack the Ripper killings of the 1880s.

headline.main: Feeling the Long Reach of Jack the Ripper in a Series of Gruesome Killings
